# Event Data Pipeline Capstone

This project implements an end-to-end data pipeline for historical and live events.

## Architecture
- Event generators (historical + live)
- MongoDB as raw landing zone
- Transformation and data quality rules
- Dimensional warehouse (BigQuery-ready)

## Tech Stack
- Python
- MongoDB
- Pandas
- BigQuery (analytical warehouse)

## Features
- Idempotent ingestion
- Late-arriving event handling
- Data quality classification
- Fact and dimension modeling